author: Morgan Phillips
title: NJ engagement party broken up by police amid coronavirus fears; child-endangerment charges filed
description: Ten people in New Jersey, including a 99-year-old man, have been charged for violating the state’s coronavirus stay-at-home order after attending an engagement party.
